[cyware_threat_intelligence_exchange://<name>]
interval_proxy = Time interval of input in minutes. Interval must be greater than 5 minutes.
saved_result_set_tag = Tag added to "Saved Result Set" Rule Action in CTIX. Leave the field blank to fetch all data
account = Select Account from where data will be fetched.
ingest_to_index = Select the checkbox to enable the data collection in index.
lookback_days = (Optional) Indicators will be collected for the specified number of past days from Cyware (default 30 days).
enrich_data = Select the checkbox to enable the enrichment of data.
